{"tid":678802,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"如何面對 雲加跟你走過的日子現在剩下我獨行，如何用歌聲一一講你知","createTime":"2018-05-26T11:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T15:00:25.000Z","uid":36497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a2d4c62d483f92c5bb3fe42f1b2ed1396ff595ba","tid":678802,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T11:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/192142_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F192142_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=83a2fa2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如何面對 雲加跟你走過的日子<br />\n現在剩下我獨行<br />\n如何用歌聲一一講你知<br />\n從來沒人明白我<br />\n雲加你給我好日子<br />\n有你有我有情有生有死有義！<br />\n<br />\n多少風波都願闖<br />\n只因雲加不死的目光<br />\n有你有我有情有天有海有地<br />\n<br />\n不可猜測總有天意<br />\n才珍惜歐聯的日子<br />\n道別話亦未多講<br />\n只拋低這個傷心的雲加<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雲加去了 誰分享不敗的日子<br />\n活著但是沒靈魂<br />\n才明白生死之間的意思<br />\n<br />\n情濃雲加明白了<br />\n才甘心披上孤獨衣<br />\n有你有我有情有天有海有地<br />\n<br />\n當天一起不自知<br />\n分開方知根本心極癡<br />\n有你有我有情有生有死有義<br />\n<br />\n只想解釋反雲不智<br />\n如今想傾訴講誰知<br />\n剩下雲加舊身影<br />\n今只得千億傷心的句子<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804411cec102e19ba11965c8aba0dee3a43c741c","tid":678802,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T11:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b24ae6ae6d70f2f6b04056eac6e984dc818b80d","tid":678802,"uid":79005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T11:30:08.000Z","msg":"樓主真迷雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c34e905f171b66894e61299953208fb90371d74","tid":678802,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b24ae6ae6d70f2f6b04056eac6e984dc818b80d","tid":678802,"uid":79005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T11:30:08